    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-rules.8LYPguczQUxUtxHF]{UM5 Ch.6: Armor}</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">This is a light, but still somewhat clumsy collection of ceramic and polymer plates placed strategically to withstand impacts without hampering maneuverability significantly. This armor works well under normal clothes without revealing its purpose.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Resistance (Mk2):&nbsp;</strong>You have resistance to slashing from nonmagical weapons.</span></p>\n<table class=\"NormalTable\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Ballistics Armor, Mk 2 </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"color: #242021;\">800 </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">12+Dex modifier </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">— </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">— </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">15 lb. </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">— </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">0</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
